How to generate documentations
==============================

All document files are written in Markdown syntax which can be easily converted to HTML or a PDF files. To render a PDF file either *pandoc* or *gimli* may be used. 


Gimli installation
------------------

With a debian distribution gimli may be install with the following commands:

      $ apt-get install ruby rubygems wkhtmltopdf libxml2-dev libxslt-dev
      $ gem install gimli


PDF Generation
--------------

We can now convert our Markdown file to a PDF document. In the current folder type:

      $ make
